text: Yemeni Canadians are Canadians of Yemeni descent or Yemenis who have Canadian citizenship. Most Yemeni Canadians speak Arabic, English or French. According to the 2016 Census there were 6,645 Canadians who claimed Yemeni ancestry. ==See also== * Arab Canadians * Yemeni Americans == References == == External links == * Category:Arab Canadian Canadian
title: Yemeni Canadians
